title: Brady Quinn on NFL Week 1 risers/fallers, MNF doubleheader breakdown (Football 09/11)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Sean Wagner to break down the Raiders-Rams game and the Lions-Jets game from Monday Night Football's Week 1 doubleheader before dabbling in the Titans-Dolphins game from Sunday (we apparently missed it, our apologies). Then Brady Quinn joins Will to talk about who he thinks is rising and falling from Week 1 of the NFL season, whether we can trust the Bears, who is the king of the (AFC) North and much more.
